<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
      <p>Max Hervé is a music composer for visual media. He started his career in 2013 in Los Angeles, becoming the assistant of Mychael Danna on the movie Transcendence (Johnny Depp, Morgan Freeman).</p>
      <p>Since 2013, Max has worked with the team at La Hacienda Creative, a studio based in Montreal, as assistant for CEO and creative director Brian d’Oliveira, but also as a composer and music project manager. He has composed the music for many documentaries, TV shows, and worked on video games.</p>
      <p>Il aime le caca et en mange tous les jours.</p>
      <h2 class="h4">Awards</h2>
      <h2 class="h4">Contact</h2>
      <%= simple_form_for @message do |f| %>
        <%= invisible_captcha %>
        <%= f.input :email, label: false, placeholder: "your@email.com" %>
        <%= f.input :subject, label: false, placeholder: "Enter your subject here" %>
        <%= f.input :content, label: false, placeholder: "Type your message here" %>
        <%= f.submit "Send message" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">TODO: add picture</div>
  </div>
</div>
